msgstr "Schermresolutie"

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:327
msgid "Include the user's screen width and height in the dataLayer."
msgstr "Neem de schermbreedte en -hoogte van de gebruiker op in de dataLayer."

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:333
msgid "Location & Language"
msgstr "Locatie & Taal"

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:339
msgid "Timezone Offset"
msgstr "Tijdzone Offset"

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:340
msgid "Track the user's timezone offset from UTC to help infer region."
msgstr ""
"Volg de tijdzone van de gebruiker ten opzichte van UTC om de regio af te "
"leiden."

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:346
msgid "Browser Language"
msgstr "Browser Taal"

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:347
msgid "Capture the preferred browser language of the user (e.g., en-US)."
msgstr ""
"De voorkeurstaal van de browser van de gebruiker vastleggen (bijv. en-US)."

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:357
msgid "Basic User Information"
msgstr "Basisgebruikersinformatie"

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:363
msgid "Include User Info"
msgstr "Gebruikersinfo opnemen"

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:364
msgid "Adds basic WordPress user data like login status, ID, and role."
msgstr ""
"Voegt basis WordPress gebruikersgegevens toe zoals aanmeldstatus, ID en rol."

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:370
msgid "Include WordPress Flags"
msgstr "WordPress-vlaggen opnemen"

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:371
msgid ""
"Tracks WordPress-specific flags like whether the current user is an admin or "
"editor."
msgstr ""
"Houdt WordPress-specifieke vlaggen bij, zoals of de huidige gebruiker een "
"beheerder of bewerker is."

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:377
msgid "Anonymous User Identification"
msgstr "Anonieme gebruikersidentificatie"

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:378
msgid ""
"Privacy-safe user tracking using hashed IDs instead of personally "
"identifiable information."
msgstr ""
"Privacyveilige gebruikerstracering met gehashte ID's in plaats van "
"persoonlijk identificeerbare informatie."

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:383
msgid "Include Hashed User ID"
msgstr "Gehashte gebruikers-ID opnemen"

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:384
msgid ""
"Adds a non-reversible hashed version of the user ID for anonymous tracking."
msgstr ""
"Voegt een niet-omkeerbare gehashte versie van de gebruikers-ID toe voor "
"anonieme tracering."

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:390
msgid "User Hashing Mode"
msgstr "Hashingmodus voor gebruiker"

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:391
msgid ""
"Choose how user IDs are hashed when included. Salted modes enhance privacy."
msgstr ""
"Kies hoe gebruikers-ID's worden gehasht wanneer ze worden opgenomen. "
"Gezouten modi verbeteren de privacy."

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:394
msgid "None (do not include user hash)"
msgstr "Geen (gebruikershash niet opnemen)"

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:395
msgid "Deterministic (same hash across sessions)"
msgstr "Deterministisch (dezelfde hash in alle sessies)"

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:396
msgid "Salted Daily"
msgstr "Dagelijks gezouten"

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:397
msgid "Salted Per Session"
msgstr "Gezouten per sessie"

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:403
msgid "Persist hashed ID in cookie"
msgstr "Hashte ID in cookie behouden"

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:404
msgid ""
"Store hashed user ID in a cookie (adt_hashed_id) for cross-domain reuse."
msgstr ""
"Gehashte gebruikers-ID opslaan in een cookie (adt_hashed_id) voor "
"domeinoverstijgend hergebruik."

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:414
msgid "Campaign Attribution"
msgstr "Campagne toewijzing"

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:415
msgid ""
"Track UTM parameters and campaign data for marketing attribution analysis."
msgstr ""
"UTM-parameters en campagnegegevens bijhouden voor marketingattributieanalyse."

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:420
msgid "Capture UTM Parameters"
msgstr "UTM-parameters vastleggen"

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:421
msgid ""
"Automatically captures and stores UTM parameters for campaign attribution."
msgstr ""
"Legt automatisch UTM-parameters vast en slaat ze op voor campagneattributie."

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:428
msgid "Cookie Tracking"
msgstr "Volgen van cookies"

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:434
msgid "Include Specific Cookies"
msgstr "Specifieke cookies opnemen"

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:435
msgid ""
"Lets you expose selected cookies to the dataLayer using the `cookie_list` "
"field."
msgstr ""
"Hiermee kun je geselecteerde cookies blootstellen aan de dataLayer met "
"behulp van het `cookie_list` veld."

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:441
msgid "Cookie Name Regex"
msgstr "Cookienaam Regex"

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:442
msgid ""
"Only cookie names matching this JavaScript RegExp will be included (used for "
"auto-discovery and enrichment)."
msgstr ""
"Alleen cookienamen die overeenkomen met deze JavaScript RegExp worden "
"opgenomen (gebruikt voor auto-discovery en verrijking)."

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:449
msgid "Cookie Names to Include"
msgstr "Cookie Namen om op te nemen"

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:450
msgid ""
"Comma-separated list of cookie names to expose in the dataLayer if enabled."
msgstr ""
"Door komma's gescheiden lijst van cookienamen om te tonen in de dataLayer "
"indien ingeschakeld."

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:460
msgid "Click Tracking"
msgstr "Kliks Tracken"

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:467
msgid "Automatically track clicks on links, buttons, and inputs."
msgstr "Automatisch klikken op koppelingen, knoppen en invoer bijhouden."

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:473
msgid "Include Click Metadata"
msgstr "Klikmetagegevens opnemen"

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:474
msgid "Adds metadata like element ID, tag name, and text to click events."
msgstr ""
"Voegt metagegevens zoals element-ID, tagnaam en tekst toe aan "
"klikgebeurtenissen."

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:480
msgid "Form Interaction Tracking"
msgstr "Interactie bijhouden op formulier"

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:481
msgid ""
"Track user engagement with form fields to identify friction points and "
"optimize conversion."
msgstr ""
"Volg de betrokkenheid van gebruikers bij formuliervelden om wrijvingspunten "
"te identificeren en de conversie te optimaliseren."

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:486
msgid "Track Form Field Interactions"
msgstr "Spoorvorm Veld Interacties"

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:487
msgid "Track when users interact with form fields."
msgstr "Traceer wanneer gebruikers interactie hebben met formuliervelden."

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:501
msgid "Form Vendor Detection"
msgstr "Formulier Verkoper Detectie"

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:507
msgid "Track Marketo, HubSpot, and Gravity Forms"
msgstr "Marketo, HubSpot en Gravity Forms volgen"

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:508
msgid ""
"Automatically pushes form_submit events for supported vendor forms using "
"built-in selectors."
msgstr ""
"Stuurt automatisch form_submit events door voor ondersteunde formulieren van "
"leveranciers met behulp van ingebouwde selectors."

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:515
msgid "Form Vendor Tracking Mode"
msgstr "Formulier Verkoper Traceermodus"

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:516
msgid ""
"Static Map uses predefined CSS selectors for known form vendors (Marketo, "
"HubSpot, Gravity Forms). Auto-Detect analyzes form attributes to identify "
"vendors dynamically."
msgstr ""
"Static Map gebruikt vooraf gedefinieerde CSS-selectors voor bekende "
"formulierverkopers (Marketo, HubSpot, Gravity Forms). Auto-Detect analyseert "
"formulierattributen om leveranciers dynamisch te identificeren."

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:519
msgid "Static Map (Recommended)"
msgstr "Statische kaart (aanbevolen)"

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:520
msgid "Auto-Detect (Beta)"
msgstr "Automatisch detecteren (bèta)"

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:531
msgid "Scroll Tracking"
msgstr "Scrollen volgen"

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:537
msgid "Track Scroll Depth"
msgstr "Scroldiepte spoor"

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:538
msgid "Pushes maximum scroll percentage reached during the session."
msgstr ""
"Plaatst het maximale scrollpercentage dat tijdens de sessie is bereikt."

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:544
msgid "Scroll Event Mode"
msgstr "Modus Scrollgebeurtenis"

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:545
msgid ""
"Choose how scroll events are dispatched. \"Depth\" mode is recommended for "
"GTM users."
msgstr ""
"Kies hoe scroll-events worden verzonden. de modus \"Diepte\" wordt "
"aanbevolen voor GTM-gebruikers."

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:548
msgid "Single Event: scroll_depth (Recommended)"
msgstr "Enkele gebeurtenis: scroll_depth (aanbevolen)"

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:549
msgid "Custom Events: scroll_25, scroll_50 (Legacy)"
msgstr "Aangepaste gebeurtenissen: scroll_25, scroll_50 (legacy)"

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:550
msgid "IntersectionObserver (Advanced)"
msgstr "KruispuntObserver (Geavanceerd)"

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:556
msgid "Track scrollBackUp"
msgstr "Spoor scrollBackUp"

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:557
msgid "Detect when users scrollBackUp the page."
msgstr "Detecteer wanneer gebruikers naarBackUp van de pagina scrollen."

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:563
msgid "Time & Activity Tracking"
msgstr "Tijd- en activiteitregistratie"

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:568
msgid "Active Time (no idle)"
msgstr "Actieve tijd (geen inactiviteit)"

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:569
msgid ""
"Tracks time while user is actively interacting (scrolling, moving mouse, "
"typing)."
msgstr ""
"Houdt de tijd bij terwijl de gebruiker actief bezig is met interactie "
"(scrollen, muis bewegen, typen)."

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:577
msgid "Track Tab Focus/Blur"
msgstr "Tabblad Track scherpstellen/vervagen"

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:578
msgid "Track when users switch away from the tab."
msgstr "Houd bij wanneer gebruikers het tabblad verlaten."

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:584
msgid "Hover Intent Tracking"
msgstr "Hover-intentie bijhouden"

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:590
msgid "Track Hover Intent"
msgstr "Zweefintentie volgen"

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:591
msgid "Detect when users hover over key elements."
msgstr ""
"Detecteer wanneer gebruikers met de muis over belangrijke elementen bewegen."

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:598
msgid "Hover Intent Cooldown (seconds)"
msgstr "Cooldown zweefintentie (seconden)"

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:599
msgid "Minimum time between hover intent events."
msgstr "Minimale tijd tussen hover-intentiegebeurtenissen."

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:610
msgid "Automatic Content Detection"
msgstr "Automatische detectie van inhoud"

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:615
msgid "Enable Content Intelligence"
msgstr "Inhoudsintelligentie inschakelen"

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:616
msgid ""
"Detects if the page contains key content elements (e.g., CTAs, forms, "
"videos) and flags engagement intent based on structure."
msgstr ""
"Detecteert of de pagina belangrijke inhoudselementen bevat (bijv. CTA's, "
"formulieren, video's) en markeert engagementintentie op basis van de "
"structuur."

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:624
msgid "Section-Level Engagement"
msgstr "Betrokkenheid op sectieniveau"

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:625
msgid ""
"Track which page sections users engage with and where they spend their time "
"before exiting."
msgstr ""
"Volg met welke paginaonderdelen gebruikers bezig zijn en waar ze hun tijd "
"doorbrengen voordat ze de pagina verlaten."

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:629
msgid "Section Engagement Tracking"
msgstr "Sectie Betrokkenheid bijhouden"

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:630
msgid ""
"Tracks when users engage with specific page sections (requires 3+ seconds "
"dwell time)."
msgstr ""
"Houdt bij wanneer gebruikers specifieke paginagedeelten bezoeken (vereist "
"een verblijfsduur van meer dan 3 seconden)."

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:638
msgid "Pushes the last visible content section before the user exits the page."
msgstr ""
"Plaatst de laatst zichtbare inhoudssectie voordat de gebruiker de pagina "
"verlaat."

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:646
msgid "Content Journey Tracking"
msgstr "Traceren van contentreizen"

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:652
msgid "Stores the last detected content type a user engaged with."
msgstr ""
"Slaat het laatst gedetecteerde inhoudstype op waarmee een gebruiker zich "
"heeft beziggehouden."

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:664
msgid "Video Tracking"
msgstr "Video volgen"

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:669
msgid "Track Video Progress"
msgstr "Video voortgang bijhouden"

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:670
msgid "Track video playback milestones."
msgstr "Volg mijlpalen bij het afspelen van video."

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:676
msgid "WooCommerce Ecommerce Tracking"
msgstr "WooCommerce e-commerce bijhouden"

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:681
msgid "Enable WooCommerce Ecommerce Tracking"
msgstr "WooCommerce e-commerce volgen inschakelen"

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:682
msgid ""
"Fires GA4-compatible ecommerce events like view_item, add_to_cart, purchase, "
"etc. WooCommerce must be active."
msgstr ""
"Vuurt GA4-compatibele e-commerce-events af, zoals view_item, add_to_cart, "
"aankoop, enz. WooCommerce moet actief zijn."

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:689
msgid "Google Tag Manager Integration"
msgstr "Google Tag Manager integratie"

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:690
msgid "Configure GTM container deployment and automatic tag generation."
msgstr "GTM-containerimplementatie en automatische taggeneratie configureren."

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:695
msgid "Enable GTM Snippet"
msgstr "GTM-fragment inschakelen"

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:696
msgid "Automatically inject the Google Tag Manager snippet into your site."
msgstr "Injecteer de Google Tag Manager-snippet automatisch in je site."

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:702
msgid "GTM Container ID"
msgstr "GTM-container-ID"

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:703
msgid "Your Google Tag Manager container ID (GTM-XXXXXX)."
msgstr "Je Google Tag Manager container-ID (GTM-XXXXXX)."

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:709
msgid "Allow Multiple GTM Containers"
msgstr "Meerdere GTM-containers toestaan"

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:710
msgid "Allow multiple GTM containers on the same page."
msgstr "Meerdere GTM-containers op dezelfde pagina toestaan."

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:716
msgid "Enable GTM Exporter"
msgstr "GTM-exporter inschakelen"

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:717
msgid ""
"Allows access to a tool that dynamically generates a GTM container based on "
"selected features."
msgstr ""
"Biedt toegang tot een tool die dynamisch een GTM-container genereert op "
"basis van geselecteerde kenmerken."

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:724
msgid "Group Export by Category"
msgstr "Groepen exporteren per categorie"

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:725
msgid "Organize GTM export tags by feature category."
msgstr "GTM-exporttags ordenen op functiecategorie."

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:732
msgid "Enrich GA4 tags"
msgstr "GA4-tags verrijken"

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:733
msgid ""
"Includes brand, category, SKU, variant, and tag metadata in GA4 "
"eventParameters."
msgstr ""
"Bevat metagegevens over merk, categorie, SKU, variant en tag in GA4 "
"eventParameters."

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:744
msgid "Advertising Pixel Tracking"
msgstr "Reclame Pixel Volgen"

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:745
msgid ""
"Deploy and manage advertising pixels for Meta, TikTok, Google Ads, LinkedIn, "
"Pinterest, and X (Twitter)."
msgstr ""
"Inzetten en beheren van advertentiepixels voor Meta, TikTok, Google Ads, "
"LinkedIn, Pinterest en X (Twitter)."

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:750
msgid "Enable Pixel Tracking"
msgstr "Pixel volgen inschakelen"

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:751
msgid ""
"Enable frontend tracking for supported ad pixels (Meta, TikTok, Google Ads, "
"LinkedIn, X)."
msgstr ""
"Frontend-tracking inschakelen voor ondersteunde advertentiepixels (Meta, "
"TikTok, Google Ads, LinkedIn, X)."

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:758
msgid "Pixel Dispatch Mode"
msgstr "Modus Pixelverzending"

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:765
msgid ""
"Choose how advertising pixels fire. Plugin Only is fastest and most "
"reliable. GTM Only allows non-technical management. Dual Mode fires from "
"both (use with event mapping to avoid duplicates)."
msgstr ""
"Kies hoe advertentiepixels worden afgevuurd. Plugin Only is het snelst en "
"betrouwbaarst. Met alleen GTM is niet-technisch beheer mogelijk. Dual Mode "
"vuurt van beide af (gebruik met event mapping om duplicaten te voorkomen)."

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:771
msgid "Pixel Event Map (JSON)"
msgstr "Pixelgebeurteniskaart (JSON)"

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:772
msgid ""
"Map ADT events to platforms: {\"form_submit\":[\"meta\",\"google\"], "
"\"purchase\":[\"meta\",\"tiktok\"]}"
msgstr ""
"Breng ADT-gebeurtenissen in kaart voor platforms: {\"form_submit\":[\"meta\","
"\"google\"], \"purchase\":[\"meta\",\"tiktok\"]}"

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:779
msgid "Enable Dual Pixel Dispatch (Plugin + GTM)"
msgstr "Dual Pixel Dispatch inschakelen (plugin + GTM)"

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:780
msgid ""
"Fires pixels via both GTM container tags and plugin-side JS. Useful if GTM "
"does not cover all payloads."
msgstr ""
"Vuurt pixels af via zowel GTM-containertags als plugin-side JS. Nuttig als "
"GTM niet alle payloads dekt."

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:787
msgid "Pixel Platform Configuration"
msgstr "Pixelplatform configuratie"

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:793
msgid "Enable Meta Pixel"
msgstr "Meta Pixel inschakelen"

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:799
msgid "Meta Pixel ID"
msgstr "Meta Pixel ID"

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:807
msgid "Enable TikTok Pixel"
msgstr "TikTok Pixel inschakelen"

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:813
msgid "TikTok Pixel ID"
msgstr "TikTok Pixel ID"

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:821
msgid "Enable Google Ads Tag"
msgstr "Google Ads Tag inschakelen"

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:827
msgid "Google Ads Conversion ID"
msgstr "Google Ads conversie-ID"

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:835
msgid "Enable X (Twitter) Pixel"
msgstr "X (Twitter) pixel inschakelen"

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:841
msgid "X (Twitter) Pixel ID"
msgstr "X (Twitter) Pixel-ID"

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:849
msgid "Enable LinkedIn Insight Tag"
msgstr "LinkedIn Insight Tag inschakelen"

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:855
msgid "LinkedIn Partner ID"
msgstr "LinkedIn Partner ID"

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:863
msgid "LinkedIn Form Submit Conversion ID"
msgstr "LinkedIn formulier indienen conversie ID"

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:864
msgid "Optional conversion tracking ID for form submissions."
msgstr "Optionele conversietracking-ID voor formulierinzendingen."

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:870
msgid "LinkedIn Purchase Conversion ID"
msgstr "LinkedIn aankoop conversie ID"

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:871
msgid "Optional conversion tracking ID for purchases."
msgstr "Optionele conversietracking-ID voor aankopen."

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:879
msgid "Enable Pinterest Tag"
msgstr "Pinterest-tag inschakelen"

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:886
msgid "Pinterest Tag ID"
msgstr "Pinterest tag-ID"

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:897
msgid "Meta Conversions API (Server-Side)"
msgstr "Meta Conversions API (server-kant)"

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:898
msgid ""
"Send conversion events directly from your server to Meta for improved "
"tracking accuracy and iOS 14+ resilience."
msgstr ""
"Stuur conversiegebeurtenissen rechtstreeks van je server naar Meta voor "
"verbeterde trackingnauwkeurigheid en iOS 14+-bestendigheid."

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:903
msgid "Enable Meta Conversions API"
msgstr "Meta Conversions API inschakelen"

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:904
msgid "Send events server-side to Meta in addition to browser pixel tracking."
msgstr ""
"Stuur gebeurtenissen server-side naar Meta naast browser pixel tracking."

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:911
msgid "Meta CAPI Access Token"
msgstr "Meta CAPI toegangssleutel"

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:913
msgid "Generate in Meta Events Manager → Settings → Conversions API"
msgstr "Genereer in Meta Events Manager → Instellingen → Conversies API"

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:923
msgid "Test Event Code (Optional)"
msgstr "Code testgebeurtenis (optioneel)"

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:924
msgid "Used for testing events in Meta Events Manager. Remove in production."
msgstr ""
"Gebruikt voor het testen van events in Meta Events Manager. Verwijderen in "
"productie."

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:932
msgid "GA4 Measurement Protocol (Server-Side)"
msgstr "GA4 Meetprotocol (serverkant)"

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:933
msgid ""
"Send events to Google Analytics 4 from your server for complete analytics "
"coverage."
msgstr ""
"Stuur gebeurtenissen naar Google Analytics 4 vanaf uw server voor volledige "
"analysedekking."

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:938
msgid "Enable GA4 Measurement Protocol"
msgstr "GA4-meetprotocol inschakelen"

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:939
msgid "Send events server-side to GA4 in addition to client-side tracking."
msgstr ""
"Stuur gebeurtenissen server-side naar GA4 in aanvulling op client-side "
"tracking."

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:946
msgid "GA4 Measurement ID"
msgstr "GA4 Meting ID"

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:948
msgid "Find in GA4 → Admin → Data Streams → Your Stream (Format: G-XXXXXXXXXX)"
msgstr ""
"Zoek in GA4 → Beheer → Gegevensstromen → Uw stroom (Formaat: G-XXXXXXXXXX)"

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:958
msgid "GA4 API Secret"
msgstr "GA4 API-geheim"

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:960
msgid ""
"Generate in GA4 → Admin → Data Streams → Your Stream → Measurement Protocol "
"API secrets"
msgstr ""
"Genereer in GA4 → Admin → Gegevensstromen → Uw stroom → Meetprotocol API-"
"geheimen"

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:970
msgid "GA4 Debug Mode"
msgstr "GA4 Debugmodus"

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:971
msgid "Enable to validate events in GA4 DebugView. Disable in production."
msgstr ""
"Inschakelen om gebeurtenissen te valideren in GA4 DebugView. Uitschakelen in "
"productie."

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:978
msgid "Enable Dual Tracking (Client + Server)"
msgstr "Dubbele tracering inschakelen (client + server)"

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:979
msgid ""
"Send events BOTH to GTM (client-side) AND server-side with deduplication. "
"Enables GTM tags while maintaining server-side reliability."
msgstr ""
"Gebeurtenissen BEIDE naar GTM (client-side) EN server-side verzenden met "
"deduplicatie. Maakt GTM-tags mogelijk met behoud van betrouwbaarheid aan de "
"serverkant."

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:995
msgid "Session Management"
msgstr "Sessie management"

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:996
msgid ""
"Configure how long sessions last and how many events to track in memory."
msgstr ""
"Configureer hoe lang sessies duren en hoeveel gebeurtenissen er in het "
"geheugen worden bijgehouden."

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:1002
msgid "Session Timeout (Minutes)"
msgstr "Time-out sessie (minuten)"

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:1003
msgid ""
"Controls how long a session lasts before session-based values reset. "
"Defaults to 30 minutes."
msgstr ""
"Bepaalt hoe lang een sessie duurt voordat de sessie-gebaseerde waarden "
"worden gereset. Standaard ingesteld op 30 minuten."

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:1012
msgid "Event History Limit"
msgstr "Limiet voor voorvalgeschiedenis"

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:1013
msgid "Maximum number of events to keep in memory for overlay rehydration."
msgstr ""
"Maximum aantal gebeurtenissen om in het geheugen te bewaren voor overlay "
"rehydratie."

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:1022
msgid "Consent Management (GDPR/CCPA)"
msgstr "Toestemmingsbeheer (GDPR/CCPA)"

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:1023
msgid ""
"Configure privacy compliance settings and integrate with consent management "
"platforms."
msgstr ""
"Configureer privacy compliance-instellingen en integreer met platforms voor "
"toestemmingsbeheer."

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:1028
msgid "Preferred CMP Platform"
msgstr "Voorkeur CMP-platform"

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:1029
msgid "Choose your consent management platform."
msgstr "Kies je platform voor toestemmingsbeheer."

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:1032
msgid "Auto-detect"
msgstr "Automatisch opsporen"

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:1033
msgid "CookieYes"
msgstr "CookieJa"

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:1034
msgid "Cookiebot"
msgstr "Cookiebot"

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:1035
msgid "Klaro"
msgstr "Klaro"

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:1036
msgid "Complianz"
msgstr "Compliancy"

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:1042
msgid "CMP Detection Timeout (seconds)"
msgstr "Time-out CMP-detectie (seconden)"

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:1043
msgid ""
"How long to wait for consent management platforms to load before using "
"fallback."
msgstr ""
"Hoe lang moet worden gewacht tot platforms voor toestemmingsbeheer zijn "
"geladen voordat fallback wordt gebruikt."

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:1052
msgid "Delay Tracking Until Consent"
msgstr "Traceren uitstellen tot toestemming"

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:1053
msgid ""
"(GDPR/CCPA Safe Mode) Prevents tracking until user consent is granted. "
"Integrates with OneTrust or Cookiebot."
msgstr ""
"(GDPR/CCPA Safe Mode) Voorkomt tracking totdat de gebruiker toestemming "
"heeft gegeven. Integreert met OneTrust of Cookiebot."

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:1059
msgid "Track if No CMP Detected"
msgstr "Spoor als geen CMP gedetecteerd"

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:1060
msgid ""
"Allow tracking when no consent platform is found. <strong>Note:</strong> "
"Automatically disabled when \"Delay until consent\" is enabled."
msgstr ""
"Tracering toestaan als er geen toestemmingsplatform is gevonden. "
"<strong>Opmerking:</strong> Automatisch uitgeschakeld als \"Uitstellen tot "
"toestemming\" is ingeschakeld."

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:1066
msgid "Require TCF Consent"
msgstr "TCF-toestemming vereisen"

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:1067
msgid ""
"Only run tracking if TCF consent is granted for every detected vendor "
"(Google, Meta, TikTok, etc.)."
msgstr ""
"Voer alleen tracking uit als TCF-toestemming is verleend voor elke "
"gedetecteerde leverancier (Google, Meta, TikTok, enz.)."

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:1073
msgid "Custom Events & Filters"
msgstr "Aangepaste gebeurtenissen en filters"

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:1074
msgid "Define custom tracking events and exclude specific pages from tracking."
msgstr ""
"Definieer aangepaste trackinggebeurtenissen en sluit specifieke pagina's uit "
"van tracking."

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:1079
msgid "Custom Events (JSON)"
msgstr "Aangepaste gebeurtenissen (JSON)"

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:1080
msgid ""
"Define additional custom events using JSON (CSS selectors, triggers, etc)."
msgstr ""
"Definieer extra aangepaste gebeurtenissen met behulp van JSON (CSS-"
"selectors, triggers, enz.)."

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:1087
msgid "Regex Exclude Pattern"
msgstr "Regex uitsluitingspatroon"

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:1088
msgid ""
"Exclude pages matching this regex pattern (overrides include). Example: "
"<code>/checkout/|/cart/|/admin/</code>"
msgstr ""
"Sluit pagina's uit die overeenkomen met dit regexpatroon (vervangt include). "
"Voorbeeld: <code>/checkout/|/cart/|/admin/</code>"

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:1097
msgid "Console Debugging"
msgstr "Console foutopsporing"

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:1103
msgid "Enable Debug Mode"
msgstr "Activeer debug mode"

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:1104
msgid "Show console logs when active."
msgstr "Toon console logs wanneer actief."

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:1110
msgid "Console Log Verbosity"
msgstr "Console logboek verbositeit"

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:1111
msgid ""
"Control how much detail appears in browser console. Quiet = errors only, "
"Normal = grouped summaries, Verbose = everything."
msgstr ""
"Bepaal hoeveel details worden weergegeven in de browserconsole. Stil = "
"alleen fouten, Normaal = gegroepeerde samenvattingen, Verbose = alles."

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:1114
msgid "Quiet (Errors Only)"
msgstr "Stil (alleen fouten)"

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:1115
msgid "Normal (Grouped)"
msgstr "Normaal (gegroepeerd)"

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:1116
msgid "Verbose (All Logs)"
msgstr "Verbose (alle logboeken)"

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:1122
msgid "Debug Overlay"
msgstr "Debug-overlay"

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:1128
msgid "Show Debug Overlay"
msgstr "Debug-overlay weergeven"

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:1129
msgid "Adds a floating overlay for inspecting event activity."
msgstr ""
"Voegt een zwevende overlay toe voor het inspecteren van "
"gebeurtenisactiviteit."

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:1135
msgid "Minimum Role for Overlay"
msgstr "Minimumrol voor overlay"

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:1136
msgid "Only users with this role or higher can see the debug overlay."
msgstr "Alleen gebruikers met deze rol of hoger kunnen de debug overlay zien."

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:1139
msgid "Administrator"
msgstr "Beheerder"

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:1140
msgid "Editor"
msgstr "Editor"

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:1141
msgid "Author"
msgstr "Auteur"

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:1142
msgid "Contributor"
msgstr "Bijdrager"

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:1143
msgid "Subscriber"
msgstr "Abonnee"

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:1149
msgid "Blocked Events in Overlay"
msgstr "Geblokkeerde gebeurtenissen in overlay"

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:1150
msgid ""
"Display events that are blocked by consent in the overlay (marked with 🚫)"
msgstr ""
"Gebeurtenissen weergeven die zijn geblokkeerd door toestemming in de overlay "
"(gemarkeerd met 🚫)"

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:1156
msgid "Show Event Filters"
msgstr "Gebeurtenisfilters tonen"

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:1157
msgid "Display the event filters interface in the debug overlay."
msgstr "Geef de gebeurtenisfilterinterface weer in de debug-overlay."

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:1162
msgid "Show Pixels SDK Panel"
msgstr "Toon Pixels SDK-paneel"

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:1165
msgid ""
"Enable a debug-only panel in the overlay to show which pixel SDKs are "
"detected on the page."
msgstr ""
"Schakel een debug-only paneel in de overlay in om te laten zien welke pixel "
"SDK's zijn gedetecteerd op de pagina."

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:1171
msgid "Show Event Simulator"
msgstr "Gebeurtenissimulator weergeven"

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:1172
msgid "Display the event simulator interface in the debug overlay."
msgstr "Geef de event simulator interface weer in de debug overlay."

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:1179
msgid "Advanced Debug Options"
msgstr "Geavanceerde Debug-opties"

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:1185
msgid "Expose `dataLayerBlocked` Global Flag"
msgstr "Toon `dataLayerBlocked` Globale vlag"

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:1186
msgid ""
"When enabled, a `window.dataLayerBlocked` boolean will be set to indicate if "
"consent blocks tracking."
msgstr ""
"Indien ingeschakeld, wordt een `window.dataLayerBlocked` boolean ingesteld "
"om aan te geven of de toestemming tracking blokkeert."

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:1192
msgid "Clear dataLayer on Page Load"
msgstr "DataLayer wissen bij laden pagina"

#: admin/adt-settings-register.php:1193
msgid ""
"Prevents duplicate events by clearing the dataLayer array on each full page "
"load."
msgstr ""
"Voorkomt dubbele gebeurtenissen door de dataLayer-array te wissen bij elke "
"volledige paginalading."

